body:
```
make generated_files DBG_MAKEFILE=1
Makefile:17: ***** starting makefile for goal(s) "generated_files"
Makefile:18: ***** Wed Jul 13 21:53:53 EDT 2016
Makefile.generated_files:93: ***** finding all *.go dirs
Makefile.generated_files:160: ***** finding all +k8s: tags
Makefile.generated_files:188: ***** finding all +k8s:deepcopy-gen tags
Makefile.generated_files:296: ***** finding all +k8s:conversion-gen tags
mkdir -p .make/_output/bin;                                        \
    (echo -n "_output/bin/conversion-gen: ";                        \
     DIRECT=$(go list -e -f '{{.Dir}} {{.Dir}}/*.go' ./cmd/libs/go2idl/conversion-gen);                \
     INDIRECT=$(go list -e   -f '{{range .Deps}}{{.}}{{"\n"}}{{end}}' ./cmd/libs/go2idl/conversion-gen | grep "^k8s.io/kubernetes" | xargs go list -e -f '{{.Dir}} {{.Dir}}/*.go');  \
     echo $DIRECT $INDIRECT | sed 's/ / \\\n\t/g';       \
    ) | sed "s|$(pwd -P)/||" > .make/_output/bin/conversion-gen.mk.tmp;                    \
    cmp -s .make/_output/bin/conversion-gen.mk.tmp .make/_output/bin/conversion-gen.mk || cat .make/_output/bin/conversion-gen.mk.tmp > .make/_output/bin/conversion-gen.mk && rm -f .make/_output/bin/conversion-gen.mk.tmp
mkdir -p .make/_output/bin;                                        \
    (echo -n "_output/bin/deepcopy-gen: ";                          \
     DIRECT=$(go list -e -f '{{.Dir}} {{.Dir}}/*.go' ./cmd/libs/go2idl/deepcopy-gen);                  \
     INDIRECT=$(go list -e   -f '{{range .Deps}}{{.}}{{"\n"}}{{end}}' ./cmd/libs/go2idl/deepcopy-gen | grep "^k8s.io/kubernetes" | xargs go list -e -f '{{.Dir}} {{.Dir}}/*.go');  \
     echo $DIRECT $INDIRECT | sed 's/ / \\\n\t/g';       \
    ) | sed "s|$(pwd -P)/||" > .make/_output/bin/deepcopy-gen.mk.tmp;                    \
    cmp -s .make/_output/bin/deepcopy-gen.mk.tmp .make/_output/bin/deepcopy-gen.mk || cat .make/_output/bin/deepcopy-gen.mk.tmp > .make/_output/bin/deepcopy-gen.mk && rm -f .make/_output/bin/deepcopy-gen.mk.tmp
make: *** No rule to make target `\nt/Users/clayton/projects/go/src/k8s.io/kubernetes/cmd/libs/go2idl/deepcopy-gen/main.go', needed by `_output/bin/deepcopy-gen'.  Stop.
```

I don't know where the `\nt` at the beginning of the target comes from, but probably from assumptions about sed version that are wrong.

I had to update to gnu-sed 4.2.2 to build.
title: make on Mac breaks with a bad target for older sed
